<paragraph pageId="621" pageNumber="622">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="621" pageNumber="622">This species ranges from southern California to southwestern New Mexico, south to Oaxaca in Mexico (Bell 1960: 116).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
